column21:
Yavniel Field is the Baritone vocalist for Shir Soul a cappella.

Yavniel was born into a family of professional classical musicians and celebrates music as a special part of his life. He learned violin from a young age and later expanded his acoustic repertoire to include piano and guitar. He discovered a love of singing early on, and engages in composition, collaboration, and production as a vocalist and multi-instrumentalist.

Yavniel has been singing a cappella for 7 years, and has performed with numerous vocal ensembles. He has published an original EP of folk music, with voice, violin, and instrumental accompaniment. He currently collaborates with family, friends and colleagues on new music from his home base in Vancouver, Canada.

Yavniel is excited and grateful to be joining Shir Soul for Pesach in Las Vegas 2023!
